Package model

package model
  • Class
    Description
    Api
    This interface is made for calling API's.
    ApiImpl
    This class does the call to AlphaVantage API.
    DataStoreFromApi
    This interface contains methods to fetch,store and display the AlphaVantage API results, to reduce the number of API calls.
    DataStoreFromApiImpl
    This class implements the DataStoreFromApi interface.
    FileOperations
    This interface is used for all the file operations.
    FileOperationsImpl
    This class has all the methods for reading from and writing to a file.
    FlexiblePortfolio
    This interface is a model of flexible portfolio.
    FlexiblePortfolioImpl
    This is the class of Flexible portfolio which consists of methods to get portfolios and get and set stocks.
    Portfolio
    This interface is a model of Portfolio.
    PortfolioImpl
    This class has all the functions of Portfolio model.
    Stocks
    This interface is the model of stock.
    StocksImpl
    This class has all the functions of Stock model.
    SuperPortfolio
    This interface is the main super portfolio interface.
    Ticker
    This is an enum class consisting of ticker symbols of all the stocks listed in NASDAQ 100.
    User
    This interface is the model of user.
    UserImpl
    This class has all the functions of user model.
    UserModelExtension
    This interface extends the User Model interface and has methods to invest amounts in a portfolio according to dollar cost averaging strategy.
    UserModelExtensionImpl
    This class implements the UserModelExtension interface and extends the UserImpl class.
